metadata.name: A Kid on Earth
metadata.description: The interplay between the natural forms and the rough, concrete textures of the background creates a powerful visual narrative that speaks to the theme of the piece. Through its unique blend of materials and dynamic composition, this artwork captures the dynamic energy of street culture while also highlighting the beauty and fragility of the natural world. This thought-provoking and captivating 3D piece invites viewers to consider the relationship between nature and the urban landscape, and serves as a reminder of the importance of preserving the environment in our cities.
